<p><b>The South Alberta Light Horse</b>, or SALH, is a Reserve armoured reconnaissance regiment unit of the <a href="/wiki/Canadian_Army" title="Canadian Army">Canadian Army</a> based in <a href="/wiki/Medicine_Hat" title="Medicine Hat">Medicine Hat</a> and <a href="/wiki/Edmonton" title="Edmonton">Edmonton</a>, <a href="/wiki/Alberta" title="Alberta">Alberta</a>. The SALH is part of <a href="/wiki/Land_Force_Western_Area" title="Land Force Western Area">3rd Canadian Division</a>'s <a href="/wiki/41_Canadian_Brigade_Group" title="41 Canadian Brigade Group">41 Canadian Brigade Group</a>.</p>
<p></p>
