<h2><span class="mw-headline" id="Battle_honours">Battle honours</span></h2>
<div class="thumb tright">
<div class="thumbinner" style="width:222px;"><a href="/wiki/File:SALH_Guidon.jpg" class="image"><img alt="" src="//upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/en/thumb/1/19/SALH_Guidon.jpg/220px-SALH_Guidon.jpg" width="220" height="170" class="thumbimage" srcset="//upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/en/thumb/1/19/SALH_Guidon.jpg/330px-SALH_Guidon.jpg 1.5x, //upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/en/thumb/1/19/SALH_Guidon.jpg/440px-SALH_Guidon.jpg 2x" data-file-width="563" data-file-height="434" /></a>
<div class="thumbcaption">
<div class="magnify"><a href="/wiki/File:SALH_Guidon.jpg" class="internal" title="Enlarge"></a></div>
The guidon of the South Alberta Light Horse.</div>
</div>
</div>
<p>In the list below, battle honours in small capitals were awarded for participation in large operations and campaigns, while those in lowercase indicate honours granted for more specific battles. Those battle honours in bold type are emblazoned on the <a href="/wiki/Colours,_standards_and_guidons#Colours_in_the_cavalry_regiments" title="Colours, standards and guidons">regimental guidon</a>.</p>
<h3><span class="mw-headline" id="North_West_Rebellion">North West Rebellion</span></h3>
<ul>
<li><span class="smallcaps" style="font-variant:small-caps;"><b>North West Canada, 1885</b></span></li>
</ul>
<h3><span class="mw-headline" id="The_Great_War">The Great War</span></h3>
<div class="div-col columns column-width" style="-moz-column-width: 15em; -webkit-column-width: 15em; column-width: 15em;">
<ul>
<li><span class="smallcaps" style="font-variant:small-caps;">Ypres, <a href="/wiki/Second_Battle_of_Ypres" title="Second Battle of Ypres">1915</a>, <a href="/wiki/Battle_of_Passchendaele" title="Battle of Passchendaele"><b> '​17</b></a></span></li>
<li><a href="/wiki/Second_Battle_of_Ypres#Battle_of_Gravenstafel_.2822.E2.80.9323_April_1915.29" title="Second Battle of Ypres">Gravenstafel</a></li>
<li><a href="/wiki/Battle_of_St._Julien" title="Battle of St. Julien" class="mw-redirect">St. Julien</a></li>
<li><span class="smallcaps" style="font-variant:small-caps;"><a href="/wiki/Battle_of_Festubert" title="Battle of Festubert">Festubert, 1915</a></span></li>
<li><span class="smallcaps" style="font-variant:small-caps;"><a href="/wiki/Battle_of_Mont_Sorrel" title="Battle of Mont Sorrel"><b>Mount Sorrel</b></a></span></li>
